For deployment.

Prerequesites:
- Have a Heroku account and a Heroku app
- Install the Heroku toolbelt
- Login with Heroku:
  $ heroku login
- Copy your public key to Heroku:
  $ heroku keys:add ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub

To deploy the application run:
$ ./deploy.sh <path to node-directory> <Heroku application name>

The deployment script will output what it is doing as it works. Check the output for any issues.

Good luck!
